## 1. SBOM (mandatory)
- One SBOM per production artifact, generated each release.
- Must include direct + transitive dependencies + hashes.

## 2. VEX
- For any critical vuln not fixed immediately, publish a VEX:
  - status (not affected / fixed / under investigation / affected)
  - rationale + mitigation + review date

## 3. Vulnerability SLAs (reference)
- Critical: ≤ 7 days (baseline), ≤ 72h (regulated)
- High: ≤ 30 days

## 4. Evidence
- SBOMs, VEXs, remediation tickets.
